      "text": "This model would allow us to make sense of the involvement of a variety of members:\n\n- [[Worker members]] - those members with employment contracts - a relatively small number of people with high levels of responsibility for the interests of the members - but whose work must serve the interests of the whole membership.\n- [[Co-operative members]] - those members that are themselves incorporated co-ops - these may well be individually significant 'customers' of the platform tools, and therefore important, but whose influence should not distort the purpose or direction of the business.\n- [[Individual members]] - freelancers and other individual members - individually these may be isolated and become disengaged from governance without careful attention to their needs and connection.\n"
